{"tid":552158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子涉訛稱辦遊學團呃錢","createTime":"2018-02-06T09:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T09:19:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e05a1d2ce3d72c63f1e7795bcf3231d043d119","tid":552158,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180206/20296557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F20296557&d=aN%2FSgp5rf9qGftQVJ21ErDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=a0fdaffa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F20296557&h=0de8a0d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180206/20296557</a><br />\n<br />\n女子涉訛稱辦遊學團呃錢<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n     <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180206/large/06ls3p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180206%2Flarge%2F06ls3p03.jpg&h=4497499a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】創辦「宇興大自然學院」並獨力經營的女東主，涉於前年透過WhatsApp虛報有韓國遊學團參加者退出，以平價後補位向家長招徠，騙取7.6萬元報名費，但原來旅行社一直未收款，無法成團。女東主被控一項作出構成餌誘式廣告宣傳的營業行為罪，原定昨答辯，惟辯方稱未準備好，裁判官批評被告：「我唔敢話你有心拖延，不過明顯你係辦事不力。」<br />\n<br />\n庭上透露，被告徐紀麗（32歲，圖）涉聲稱與東瀛遊合辦遊學團，以6,500元超低價吸引4個家庭共24名「團友」報名，每家庭各付1.7萬至1.9萬元。被告獲准以2萬元現金保釋，下月5日答辯。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC5388/17<br />\n■記者羅日昇、伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"d924070f354d004d325ca34ef2285547b6af6313","tid":552158,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"遊學團六千幾去韓國係抵玩嘅<br />\n<br />\n 返大陸果d都七，八千啦"}]}